name: Cargills ESL Home Learning,Head, Shoulders, Knees, and Toes
description: The book focuses on these body parts: head, shoulders, knees, toes, eyes, ears, mouth, and nose. Kids learn to name body parts, develop gross motor skills by moving to music and following actions of the characters. By listening to the song, they will develop their memory power too.*Images for illustration purpose only, Product received may vary.
